<P>
What a Really Big Shoe: Ed Sullivan will be back on television for the first 
time since 1971, when the legendary CBS Sunday night variety series was 
canceled after 23 years. Producer-director Andrew Solt said last week he had 
purchased every episode of "The Ed Sullivan Show" and is negotiating with 
syndicators and networks for a series and a two-hour special featuring 
excerpts. BETH KLEID 
