ACCIDENTS -- LOS ANGELES; TRUCKS; AUTOMOBILE SAFETY; VEHICLE EQUIPMENT; 
EQUIPMENT FAILURES; NEGLIGENCE; PRODUCT LIABILITY; SUITS 
</P>
