</P>
<P>
Background: College instructor for 20 years. Former administrative positions 
with the cities of Huntington Beach, Garden Grove and Manhattan Beach. Was the 
1988 Democratic nominee in 42nd Congressional District. 
</P>
<P>
Issues: Opposes additional offshore drilling and supports a phase-out of 
existing wells; favors abortion rights and public funding for some abortions; 
favors a 5% minimum cut in defense spending now and about 25% by 1995; supports 
a tax increase to reduce the deficit. 
