<HEADLINE>
<P>
VENTURA COUNTY NEWS ROUNDUP: POINT MUGU; 
</P>
<P>
NAVY RESERVIST DIES IN COLLISION ON BASE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
A Navy reservist on weekend training at the Pacific Missile Test Center in 
Point Mugu died Saturday after the motorcycle he was driving collided with a 
truck on the base, authorities said. 
</P>
<P>
Daniel Ian Ross, 24, of San Gabriel was heading from a morning training class 
to another training site when his motorcycle crashed head-on with a 
contractor's truck, said Marilyn Moore, a Navy Reserve spokeswoman. 
</P>
<P>
Moore said an investigation is under way. 
</P>
</TEXT>
