<HEADLINE>
<P>
ORANGE COUNTY FOCUS: MISSION VIEJO; 
</P>
<P>
GENERAL PLAN REPORT AVAILABLE TO PUBLIC 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
The public will have a last chance Tuesday to comment on the environmental 
impact report dealing with the city's general plan. 
</P>
<P>
With just weeks left before the deadline for submitting the plan to the state, 
the Planning Commission will hear final public comments on the report at City 
Hall at 7 p.m. 
</P>
<P>
Residents wanting to review the document can examine a copy at City Hall, the 
Oso Viejo Community Center or the county library in Mission Viejo. 
</P>
</TEXT>
<TYPE>
<P>
Brief; Column 
</P>
</TYPE>
