<P>
1990 PREP WATER POLO PREVIEW 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Top Teams (In alphabetical order): Capistrano Valley, Corona del Mar, Edison, 
El Dorado, El Toro, Mission Viejo, Newport Harbor, San Clemente, Sunny Hills, 
Tustin, University, Villa Park. 
</P>
<P>
